metadata.name: The Universe is Under No Obligation
metadata.description:
Animated activation of the pithy reminder from Neil deGrasse Tyson: "The Universe is Under No Obligation to Make Sense to You." Dozens of uniquely colorful posters were made by letterpress printing antique gothic wood type in fluorescent purple over one-of-a-kind inkwipes, then shot in sequence.

Duration: 29 secs
Size: 800p x 800p
Codecs: AAC, H.264
Rate: 30fps
File: 39.6MB
No Audio
